nodes.text: Celebrate SoroSuub is an article written by Morrie Mullins as a tie in to the Living Force adventure No Place Like Home. It was published on the Wizards of the Coast website on November 27 2002 and took the form of an announcement by Miim Te'Suub on the plans for the upcoming celebration of the anniversary of the opening of production on Edic Bar by the SoroSuub Corporation.
